text: What's Up, Doc? is a 1972 romantic screwball comedy movie directed by Peter Bogdanovich and starring Barbra Streisand, Ryan O'Neal, Madeline Kahn, Kenneth Mars, Michael Murphy, Sorrell Booke, Sylvester Stallone, Randy Quaid. It was distributed by Warner Bros.. ==Other websites== * * * * Category:1972 romantic comedy movies Category:American romantic comedy movies Category:Movies directed by Peter Bogdanovich Category:Warner Bros. movies
